[correct]

setElevator(8, 8);
pos[1][3].f.img = "poison";
pos[1][3].f.trap = "poisonSwamp";
pos[7][8].f.img = "poison";
pos[7][8].f.trap = "poisonSwamp";
pos[3][8].f.antiWarp = true;

[endmap]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; マップを開いた時に必ず実行されるスクリプト
[initial]

[endinitial]
;===============================================================================
;◆イベント◆

; 初期発生イベント
events = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]

;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_1
;[exp] onObjectTrigger

@command title="Which button will you press?" cancel=true
@select text="17Ｆ" exp='tf.result = ["ラドミラの塔17Ｆ", "up"]'
@select text="15Ｆ" exp='tf.result = ["ラドミラの塔15Ｆ", "down"]'
@select text="14Ｆ" exp='tf.result = ["ラドミラの塔14Ｆ", "down"]'
@select text="11Ｆ" exp='tf.result = ["ラドミラの塔11Ｆ", "down"]'
@select text="No" exp='tf.result = void'
[ask]
[if exp='tf.result !== void']
	@elevator map=&'tf.result[0]' lift=&'tf.result[1]'
[endif]

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_2
;[exp] true

@delevent
[texton]
The floor is completely dilapidated, as if no one has been there for a long time. It is dimly lit and even feels eerie.[k]
Looking around, I see white bones scattered all over the floor. Did they all die here, unable to escape?[k]
[textoff]

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_3
;[exp] party.lastIsMove || inSearching

[if exp='game.inSearching']
	@delevent
	@getitem item=破邪の指輪
	[eventoff]
[endif]

[texton]
What appears to be human bones are scattered around. Could they belong to people involved in the construction of this tower?
 [k]
[textoff]

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_4
;[exp] party.hasItem(o.悪魔の彫像)

@wait time=800
[texton]
[リーダー f=06]「...!」[k]
Suddenly, I felt a terrifying killing intent from behind me![k]
[？？？]「It's mine... I won't let you steal it...」[k]
[textoff]
@wait time=800
@walk turn=n
@wait time=800
@monster pos=3 name=リッチキング
@callbattle bgm=crisis gameover=true escape=false
@eval exp='game.restoreMembers()'
@notice text="Defeated the Lich King!"
@delevent

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_5
;[exp] onObjectTrigger

@barrel
@damage v=&'game.curTarget.addParam("maxLife", 50)'
@notice text=&'"<p>" + game.curTarget.displayName + "<w> had max HP permanently increased by 50!"'

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_6
;[exp] onObjectTrigger

@barrel
@damage v=&'game.curTarget.addParam("speed", 2)'
@notice text=&'"<p>" + game.curTarget.displayName + "<w> had Speed permanently increased by 2!"'

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*_set_16button

@wait time=1500
@btmes off
[texton]
[リーダー f=05]「This is...!」[k]
The moment I saw the panel with the elevator buttons lined up on it, I remembered that small button.[k]
Looking closely at the panel, there is a hole that seems to fit this button perfectly.[k]
[リーダー f=06]「...」[k]
@se f=kacha
∗click∗[k]
The button fitted perfectly into the hole.[k]
...Maybe this will allow us to go to a new floor.[k]
[textoff]
@eval exp='f.floor16opened = true'
@eval exp='game.party.ejectItem(o.小さなボタン)'

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
